</problem>
<solution id="id1164491289937">
<para id="element-48">
In order to find dimensional formula, we use the expression of angular momentum :
</para>
<para id="element-49">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mi> ℓ </m:mi>
<m:mo> = </m:mo> 
